overview: Following in the tradition of TitanMen hits Laid Up and Rx: Open Wide, Triage is the feature directorial debut of the award-winning Paul Wilde. There's never a dull moment in these horny hospital halls, where the colossal cocks ache for a cure. Check in to Folsom Medical and check out the 11 hot studs ready to make your stay memorable, led by TitanMen exclusives Marco Blaze, Tony Buff, Dirk Jager and Rick van Sant.
title: Triage
